WEBVTT

00:26.401 --> 00:27.986
My name is Oh-nam Ju.

00:30.113 --> 00:31.781
I like spending time alone.

00:33.533 --> 00:34.617
It's been like that

00:35.452 --> 00:36.911
since I was a child.

00:40.790 --> 00:42.250
When I was young,

00:42.333 --> 00:44.669
the other kids
made fun of me and bullied me.

00:46.755 --> 00:47.589
Go, go, go!

00:47.672 --> 00:52.594
In the world of children, you are degraded
because of how small and chubby you are.

00:56.598 --> 00:58.224
Spin more, more, more!

01:02.687 --> 01:04.981
As I started middle school,
nothing changed.

01:05.065 --> 01:07.067
-It's mine!
-What you talking about?

01:07.150 --> 01:09.986
-I'm gonna eat it first!
-It's mine. Leave it!

01:10.070 --> 01:12.697
The only way
I was able to get along with them at all

01:13.656 --> 01:16.284
was to remain as invisible as possible.

01:17.660 --> 01:19.537
When I allowed myself to be seen,

01:19.621 --> 01:22.457
the bullying resumed
exactly where it left off.

01:33.718 --> 01:37.555
I gradually became terrified
of people's gazes on me.

01:38.890 --> 01:40.058
And I slowly

01:41.392 --> 01:43.019
disappeared completely.

01:45.438 --> 01:47.440
Nobody was around to listen to me.

01:49.776 --> 01:50.693
Except her.

01:53.154 --> 01:55.907
I love you. I love you.

01:56.741 --> 01:58.701
I love you.

02:00.453 --> 02:03.081
I love you too.

03:50.563 --> 03:55.526
MASK GIRL

03:56.653 --> 03:59.906
OH-NAM JU

04:14.963 --> 04:18.049
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

04:18.132 --> 04:22.011
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

04:22.095 --> 04:26.641
♪ Happy birthday dear mm-mmm ♪

04:27.767 --> 04:31.479
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

04:43.574 --> 04:45.994
Thanks, Remi-chan.

04:48.621 --> 04:49.539
Eh?!

04:49.622 --> 04:51.791
You even got a present for me?

04:53.584 --> 04:55.712
