but you didn't pick up once!

05:31.831 --> 05:33.499
Do you know what day it is today?

05:34.250 --> 05:35.251
Today is…

05:35.335 --> 05:36.836
-Didn't I tell you I was…
-…my birthday.

05:36.919 --> 05:39.005
