to Jeju Island with my church today?

05:39.088 --> 05:40.048
Oh, right.

05:40.548 --> 05:42.550
God, what am I supposed to do with you?!

05:43.051 --> 05:45.136
You know Du-sik, right? Mrs. Yang's son?

05:45.219 --> 05:47.680
The one who became a doctor.

05:47.764 --> 05:48.848
You know what he did?

05:48.931 --> 05:52.393
