and not going home?

17:30.466 --> 17:32.051
-Oh…
-Huh?

17:33.052 --> 17:33.886
Mmm…

17:33.969 --> 17:36.722
Forget it! See you tomorrow!
Weird as fuck.

17:37.514 --> 17:38.432
Yes, sir.

18:00.120 --> 18:00.954
Oh!

18:58.637 --> 19:00.973
Oh my God.

19:26.206 --> 19:29.376
♪ Please don't stop
The dance and that rhythm ♪

19:29.877 --> 19:33.297
♪ Please don't stop the dance
And that rhythm, ah! ♪

19:34.965 --> 19:37.968
♪ Please, please, please
Don't stop that dance and that rhythm ♪

19:38.051 --> 19:40.554
-Everyone!
-♪ Don't stop that dance, ooh! ♪

19:40.637 --> 19:42.514
Everyone.

