28:57.777 --> 28:59.112
Hey, Mask Girl!

28:59.195 --> 29:01.322
Oh, you're Mask Girl, right?

29:02.198 --> 29:05.577
Ah, I am so glad to meet you.
I, uh, I'm Handsome Monk.

29:06.661 --> 29:08.413
